name: Custom Letterpress cards
description:
Break free from email and give your friends and family the joy of receiving a hand written note with these timeless custom 1 color letterpress note cards. Cards are printed with antique wood type one at a time on 118lb soft cotton based paper using my 1926 c&p letterpress. Each card is then scored, folded and packaged with great care and arrives at your door ready to use or as a beautiful gift for a loved one.

Please include the following in the message to seller
• type choice "Saloon" or "Spa"
• choice of envelope color
• choice of ink color	
• choice of wording

Set is 15 folded cards or 15 flat cards
Folded card measures 4.25 x 5.5 (A2): 
Flat cards measure 5 x 7 (A7)
Each set comes with coordinating envelopes

1. Custom Orders are shipped within 7-14 days of your order date.
2. Please contact us if your name is over 7 characters as this is antique type and some letters may be limited.
3. With this style of printing a slight variations in color, registration and impression may occur, however this is what makes the process so special.

Prints are professionally packaged in a clear cellophane bag and are shipped flat in a rigged photo mailer.  They arrive ready to use or as a gift for another. Prints ship free in the continental us.

name: Personalized Critter note cards
description:
Looking for a fun way to add a personalized touch to your next order of thank you cards. We are now offering letterpress stationery featuring our cute and cuddly critter collection. You can add your name or a fun greeting to this set of nine cards making them uniquely you. Cards are letterpress printed in the 1 color of your choice using a 1906 c&p press on lush bright white cotton paper.

Please contact us for a copy of all available critters and font selection!

A. Choose one of 12 critters B. Select the ink color 
C. Select your typeface and verbiage 

Set includes 9/ 4-bar cards (3.5x4.87) 
Set includes coordinating white envelopes
Printed on tree-free cotton paper

1. Custom Orders are shipped within 7-14 days of your order date. 
2. Please contact us if your verbiage is over 24 characters as this is antique type and some letters may be limited. 
3. With this style of printing a slight variations in color, registration and impression may occur, however this is what makes the process so special. 
4. Two color printing is available please email for price and additional options.
